{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.007.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Victoires de David sur les Philistins, les Moabites, les Syriens, les \u00c9domites<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-14: cf. 1 Ch 18:1-13. (Ps 44; 60; 108.) 1 S 18:14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Apr\u00e8s cela, David battit les Philistins et les humilia, et il enleva de la main des Philistins les r\u00eanes de leur capitale.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.2","name":"2 Samuel 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.7.29","name":"2 Samuel 7:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.7.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il battit les Moabites, et il les mesura avec un cordeau, en les faisant coucher par terre; il en mesura deux cordeaux pour les livrer \u00e0 la mort, et un plein cordeau pour leur laisser la vie. Et les Moabites furent assujettis \u00e0 David, et lui pay\u00e8rent un tribut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.3","name":"2 Samuel 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.1","name":"2 Samuel 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>David battit Hadad\u00e9zer, fils de Rehob, roi de Tsoba, lorsqu\u2019il alla r\u00e9tablir sa domination sur le fleuve de l\u2019Euphrate.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.4","name":"2 Samuel 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.2","name":"2 Samuel 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>David lui prit mille sept cents cavaliers et vingt mille hommes de pied; il coupa les jarrets \u00e0 tous les chevaux de trait, et ne conserva que cent attelages.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.5","name":"2 Samuel 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.3","name":"2 Samuel 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Les Syriens de Damas vinrent au secours d\u2019Hadad\u00e9zer, roi de Tsoba, et David battit vingt-deux mille Syriens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.6","name":"2 Samuel 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.4","name":"2 Samuel 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>David mit des garnisons dans la Syrie de Damas. Et les Syriens furent assujettis \u00e0 David, et lui pay\u00e8rent un tribut. L\u2019\u00c9ternel prot\u00e9geait David partout o\u00f9 il allait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.7","name":"2 Samuel 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.5","name":"2 Samuel 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et David prit les boucliers d\u2019or qu\u2019avaient les serviteurs d\u2019Hadad\u00e9zer, et les apporta \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.8","name":"2 Samuel 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.6","name":"2 Samuel 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Le roi David prit encore une grande quantit\u00e9 d\u2019airain \u00e0 B\u00e9thach et \u00e0 B\u00e9rotha\u00ef, villes d\u2019Hadad\u00e9zer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.9","name":"2 Samuel 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.7","name":"2 Samuel 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Tho\u00ef, roi de Hamath, apprit que David avait battu toute l\u2019arm\u00e9e d\u2019Hadad\u00e9zer,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.10","name":"2 Samuel 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.8","name":"2 Samuel 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>et il envoya Joram, son fils, vers le roi David, pour le saluer, et pour le f\u00e9liciter d\u2019avoir attaqu\u00e9 Hadad\u00e9zer et de l\u2019avoir battu. Car Tho\u00ef \u00e9tait en guerre avec Hadad\u00e9zer. Joram apporta des vases d\u2019argent, des vases d\u2019or, et des vases d\u2019airain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.11","name":"2 Samuel 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.9","name":"2 Samuel 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le roi David les consacra \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, comme il avait d\u00e9j\u00e0 consacr\u00e9 l\u2019argent et l\u2019or pris sur toutes les nations qu\u2019il avait vaincues,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.12","name":"2 Samuel 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.10","name":"2 Samuel 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>sur la Syrie, sur Moab, sur les fils d\u2019Ammon, sur les Philistins, sur Amalek, et sur le butin d\u2019Hadad\u00e9zer, fils de Rehob, roi de Tsoba.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.13","name":"2 Samuel 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.11","name":"2 Samuel 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Au retour de sa victoire sur les Syriens, David se fit encore un nom, en battant dans la vall\u00e9e du sel dix-huit mille \u00c9domites.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.14","name":"2 Samuel 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.12","name":"2 Samuel 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il mit des garnisons dans \u00c9dom, il mit des garnisons dans tout \u00c9dom. Et tout \u00c9dom fut assujetti \u00e0 David. L\u2019\u00c9ternel prot\u00e9geait David partout o\u00f9 il allait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.15","name":"2 Samuel 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.13","name":"2 Samuel 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Hauts fonctionnaires de David<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-18: cf. 1 Ch 18:14-17. 2 S 20:23-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>David r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl, et il faisait droit et justice \u00e0 tout son peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.16","name":"2 Samuel 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.14","name":"2 Samuel 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Joab, fils de Tseruja, commandait l\u2019arm\u00e9e; Josaphat, fils d\u2019Achilud, \u00e9tait archiviste;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.17","name":"2 Samuel 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.15","name":"2 Samuel 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.008.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Tsadok, fils d\u2019Achithub, et Achim\u00e9lec, fils d\u2019Abiathar, \u00e9taient sacrificateurs; Seraja \u00e9tait secr\u00e9taire;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.18","name":"2 Samuel 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.16","name":"2 Samuel 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 8:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.008.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.009.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.8.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Benaja, fils de Jehojada, \u00e9tait chef des K\u00e9r\u00e9thiens et des P\u00e9l\u00e9thiens; et les fils de David \u00e9taient ministres d\u2019\u00e9tat.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8","name":"2 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.9.1","name":"2 Samuel 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.9.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.8.17","name":"2 Samuel 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.8.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbb481b01.73122254');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb481b01.73122254\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbb481b01.73122254","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbb481b01.73122254'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb481b01.73122254\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}